Class lame_version_t

  • java.lang.Object
    • lame.std.lame_version_t

  • public class lame_version_t
extends java.lang.Object
    typedef struct { // generic LAME version int major; int minor; int alpha; // 0 if not an alpha version int beta; // 0 if not a beta version // version of the psy model int psy_major; int psy_minor; int psy_alpha; // 0 if not an alpha version int psy_beta; // 0 if not a beta version // compile time features const char *features; // Don't make assumptions about the contents! } lame_version_t;
